(13965, 667, 'features_tier_one', '<h1 data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"100\">How Monnify caters to Wallet/Betting Companies</h1>\r\n<p data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"200\">Monnify provides a unique and convenient way for your customers to top up their wallets. By simply dialing a USSD code or transferring funds to a saved beneficiary on their bank app, your customers can bet on the go, online and offline. As a betting company using Monnify, you enjoy the most competitive transaction fees obtainable, instant settlements on all transactions and easy reconciliation</p>'),
