(18829, 256, 'features_tier_one', '<h1 data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"100\">How Monnify caters to Logistics Companies</h1>\r\n<p data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"200\">Monnify offers more payment options to your customers when booking a flight on your website and in-person at the airport including bank transfers with instant notifications, card payments and USSD. Monnify also guarantees you instant settlement on all transactions and gives you access to your settlement reports whenever you need.</p>'),
